FICTION is a bellisima production by composer Yuki Kajiura. In this album you will find re-arrangements of items belonging to different series as well as unreleased songs ... The voices that we see are: Emily Bidinger (tracks 1,2,3,4,5 and 10), Yuri Kasahara (tracks 6 and 12), Deb Lyons (tracks 7 and 11), Kaori Nishina (tracks 9 and 9) , finally: Tulivu-Donna Cumberbatch to Lullaby (track 13) ..
